          <p data-reveal style="--d:.12s" class="relative mt-5 text-[clamp(15px,1.2vw,18px)] text-white/65 max-w-[520px] mx-auto">Book a 30-minute call with a senior AI engineer. We'll tell you honestly what's feasible, what it takes, and where the ROI is.</p>

